  "Do we need to ingest commission-relevant data from multiple systems (CRM, ERP, HRIS, billing)?",
  "How important is real-time commission visibility for our reps?",
  "What are our audit and compliance requirements for commission documentation?",
  "Do we change commission plans mid-year, and how disruptive is that process currently?",
  "What is our budget for commission management tooling, including implementation costs?",
